<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>FAQ - Blog Post</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include("navbar") %>

    <div class="container " style="margin: 6rem auto;">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        What is a Blog Post?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        A blog post is an article or entry written by an author on a blog. It can cover various topics and is usually displayed in reverse chronological order.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                        How do I create a blog post?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        To create a blog post, log in to your account, navigate to the "Create Post" section, and fill in the required fields such as title, content, and tags. Once you're done, click "Publish" to make your post live.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Can I edit my blog post after publishing?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Yes, you can edit your blog post after publishing. Simply go to your post, click the "Edit" button, make the necessary changes, and save your updates.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                        How can I increase the visibility of my blog post?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        To increase the visibility of your blog post, you can share it on social media, use relevant tags, engage with your audience through comments, and optimize your content for search engines (SEO).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("footer") %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>